        </div>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-red-50/50 rounded-r">
          <p class="text-sm font-black text-red-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</p>
